🚀 TaskResult kya hai?
👉 Ye object hota hai jo task/job run hone ke baad uska result store karta hai
💡 Simple Definition:-
👉 TaskResult = “Task chalne ke baad kya hua uska full report”

🔥 Isme kya-kya hota hai?
Task success ya fail hua,
Kitna time laga
Output kya aaya
Errors aaye ya nahi.

🚀 TaskResult – Correct Methods List:-
getId()
getName()
getStatus()
setStatus(String status)
getCompletionStatus()
setCompletionStatus(String status)

getStartTime()
setStartTime(Date date)
getEndTime()
setEndTime(Date date)
getLaunched()
setLaunched(Date date)
getCompleted()
setCompleted(Date date)
getMessages()
addMessage(Message message)
clearMessages()

getErrors()
addError(Message message)
clearErrors()
getWarnings()
addWarning(Message message)
clearWarnings()
getProgress()
setProgress(int progress)

getPercentComplete()
setPercentComplete(int percent)
getAttributes()
setAttributes(Map attributes)
getAttribute(String key)
setAttribute(String key, Object value)
getArguments()
setArguments(Map args)

getHost()
setHost(String host)
getPartition()
setPartition(String partition)
getRetryCount()
setRetryCount(int count)
getMaxRetries()
setMaxRetries(int max)

isSuccess()
isCompleted()
isRunning()
isFailed()
toXml()
fromXml(String xml)
toMap()
fromMap(Map map)

validate()

clone()
equals(Object obj)
hashCode()
toString()
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
()🚀 1️⃣ getStatus() ke Status (Execution Status)
👉 Ye batata hai task abhi kis state me hai
Pending
Running
Completed
Failed
Cancelled
Terminated
Paused
Queued
Retrying
🚀 2️⃣ getCompletionStatus() ke Status (Final Result)
👉 Ye batata hai task ka final outcome kya hua
Success
Error
Warning
PartialSuccess
Completed
Failed
----------------------------------------------------------------
()🔹 Pending:-
👉 Task create ho gaya hai but abhi start nahi hua,
Example: Schedule kiya hai, time aane ka wait ho raha hai.

()🔹 Running:-
👉 Task abhi execute ho raha hai,
Example: Identity aggregation chal raha hai.

()🔹 Completed:-
👉 Task successfully finish ho gaya (execution complete)
Example: Aggregation pura ho gaya.

()🔹 Failed:-
👉 Task run hua but beech me error aaya aur ruk gaya,
Example: DB connection fail ho gaya.

()🔹 Cancelled:-
👉 User ya system ne task ko manually stop kar diya,
Example: Admin ne cancel button dabaya.

()🔹 Terminated:-
👉 Forcefully system ne task ko kill kar diya,
Example: Server crash ya timeout.

()🔹 Paused:-
👉 Task temporarily rok diya gaya hai,
Example: Maintenance ke liye pause.

()🔹 Queued:-
👉 Task queue me hai, run hone ka wait kar raha hai,
Example: Multiple tasks line me lage hain.

()🔹 Retrying:-
👉 Task fail hua tha, ab dobara try ho raha hai,
Example: Provisioning retry ho raha hai.

🔹 Success:-
👉 Task successfully complete ho gaya bina error ke
Example: Sab accounts successfully create ho gaye

🔹 Error:-
👉 Task complete hua but errors aaye
Example: Kuch accounts create hue, kuch fail ho gaye

🔹 Warning:-
👉 Task complete hua but minor issues aaye
Example: Kuch optional data missing tha

🔹 PartialSuccess:-
👉 Task ka kuch part successful hua, kuch fail
Example: 100 me se 70 users ka provisioning success

🔹 Completed:-
👉 Generic completion (kabhi-kabhi success ke jagah use hota hai)
Example: Task finish ho gaya (detail status alag check karna padega)

🔹 Failed:-
👉 Task final me fail ho gaya
Example: Task pura hi fail ho gaya
