2️⃣ getName():-
👉 Task ka naam (result ka naam) deta hai
System.out.println(result.getName());
Output:-
Identity Aggregation Task Result

3️⃣ getStatus():-
👉 Current execution status deta hai
System.out.println(result.getStatus());
Output:-
Completed
(aur ho sakta hai: Running, Failed)

4️⃣ setStatus(String status):-
👉 Status ko manually set karta hai
result.setStatus("Failed");
System.out.println(result.getStatus());
Output:-
Failed

5️⃣ getCompletionStatus():-
👉 Final result ka detail status deta hai
System.out.println(result.getCompletionStatus());
Output:-
Success
(ya: Error, Warning)

6️⃣ setCompletionStatus(String status):-
👉 Final completion result set karta hai
result.setCompletionStatus("Error");
System.out.println(result.getCompletionStatus());
Output:-
Error

