🚀 Partition kya hai?
👉 Partition = task ka chhota hissa (part)
👉 Jab ek bada task hota hai, usko multiple parts me tod diya jata hai taaki wo fast run ho

💡 Simple Definition:-
👉 Partition = “task ka ek piece jo alag se execute hota hai”

🔥 Real Example:-
👇 Without Partition:-
1000 users process karne hain
→ ek hi thread me chalega
→ slow hoga

👇 With Partition:-
1000 users
→ 4 partitions

Partition 1 → 250 users
Partition 2 → 250 users
Partition 3 → 250 users
Partition 4 → 250 users
👉 Sab parallel chalenge = 🔥 fast execution
